### 1. Introduction

The Project Graph is the defining visual feature of Project Sarthi.

However, its purpose is not to display every relationship inside a software project.

Its purpose is to improve understanding.

Every design decision in the graph visualization should answer one question:

**"Will this help the developer understand the project faster?"**

If the answer is no, the information probably does not belong in the graph.

