#### GP-001

Project Sarthi understands software.

It does not merely display software.

---

#### GP-002

Understanding is more valuable than organization.

The platform should explain relationships rather than collect information.

---

#### GP-003

Automation is preferred over manual input.

Developers should spend time building software, not maintaining Project Sarthi.

---

#### GP-004

Every visualization must answer a meaningful engineering question.

Visualizations are tools for understanding.

They are never decorative.

---

#### GP-005

Every major feature must reduce cognitive load.

